请仔细考虑是否要上车.<br /><br />上车请在评论区留下你的 vx<br /><br />依照楼层顺序上车, 坐满关门. 周六发车, 具体时间群内通知~","last_modified":1655083017,"replies":14,"id":859188},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":185953,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3493,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":209579,"username":"znwindy","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/znwindy","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/36f4/dd35/209579_mini.png?m=1640842414","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/36f4/dd35/209579_normal.png?m=1640842414","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/36f4/dd35/209579_large.png?m=1640842414","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/36f4/dd35/209579_xlarge.png?m=1640842414","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/36f4/dd35/209579_xlarge.png?m=1640842414","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/36f4/dd35/209579_xlarge.png?m=1640842414","created":1483757394,"last_modified":1640842414},"last_reply_by":"znwindy","last_touched":1655088536,"title":"搭建小型企业官网选什么方案求推荐？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/859209","created":1655085825,"deleted":0,"content":"最近帮一位亲戚弄企业邮箱和官网，\r\n其是小微型企业，之前一直是国内的生意，现在想开拓外单。\r\n上周帮他在阿里云万网上面买了个域名，绑定企业微信后搞好了企业邮箱。\r\n\r\n那么现在在想用什么给他搞官网（ B2B 类型的网站，不在线卖产品，主要是宣传品牌和服务联系方式等等），\r\n结合我的认知：\r\nGithub pages 、Hexo 等等虽然免费但是不太适合，也不太想搞甲骨云的服务器，不知道啥时候就会挂掉。\r\n估计就弄个阿里云或者腾讯云的弹性服务器带固定 IP 安装 WordPress 或者 Shopify 或者 Wix ，请问大家有什么推荐的吗？\r\n我尽量想我帮他弄完稍微教一下他就自己去维护，在这个基础上尽量便宜点。","content_rendered":"<p>最近帮一位亲戚弄企业邮箱和官网，\n其是小微型企业，之前一直是国内的生意，现在想开拓外单。\n上周帮他在阿里云万网上面买了个域名，绑定企业微信后搞好了企业邮箱。</p>\n<p>那么现在在想用什么给他搞官网（ B2B 类型的网站，不在线卖产品，主要是宣传品牌和服务联系方式等等），\n结合我的认知：\nGithub pages 、Hexo 等等虽然免费但是不太适合，也不太想搞甲骨云的服务器，不知道啥时候就会挂掉。\n估计就弄个阿里云或者腾讯云的弹性服务器带固定 IP 安装 WordPress 或者 Shopify 或者 Wix ，请问大家有什么推荐的吗？\n我尽量想我帮他弄完稍微教一下他就自己去维护，在这个基础上尽量便宜点。</p>\n","last_modified":1655085825,"replies":13,"id":859209},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785","name":"life","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785","title":"生活","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","topics":3217,"footer":"","header":"生活中的技术讨论","title_alternative":"Life","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","stars":844,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":557,"parent_node_name":""},"member":{"id":132693,"username":"fyxtc","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fyxtc","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/efd6/53c4/132693_mini.png?m=1646359299","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/efd6/53c4/132693_normal.png?m=1646359299","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/efd6/53c4/132693_large.png?m=1646359299","created":1439434181,"last_modified":1646359299},"last_reply_by":"HammondY5an","last_touched":1655085183,"title":"重疾险，有必要买吗","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/859187","created":1655082479,"deleted":0,"content":"年费 5000 保 50w ，一直在纠结。本地惠民保医疗险和寿险都买了，就是这个重疾开销最大也最纠结","content_rendered":"年费 5000 保 50w ，一直在纠结。本地惠民保医疗险和寿险都买了，就是这个重疾开销最大也最纠结","last_modified":1655082479,"replies":12,"id":859187},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_large.png?m=1649080598","name":"macos","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_normal.png?m=1649080598","title":"macOS","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","topics":18565,"footer":"<a href=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。","header":"The world’s most ad